name: I.A.N.Y.
description:
Iany is a Swordmaster of Cape Verde, who seeks to avenge her parents, killed by a big-tech of artificial intelligence. With her speaking sword, she departs on a mission to find clues and solve this pendency with the past.
Iany is a character from a college animation project called NIGRUM, and you can find it here: https://youtu.be/46djYPMfjkc
